title: Woman In Lotus Position Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: A woman with a medium-light skin tone sits in a meditative lotus position, representing tranquility, inner peace, and a moment of calm.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the woman in lotus position emoji with a medium-light skin tone embodies serenity and mindfulness, depicted in a graceful seated posture. Apple's design emphasizes smooth lines and gentle shading, creating a tranquil and balanced visual. This emoji is excellent for conveying peace, meditation, yoga, or a moment of calm reflection.
